Zambia’s Lubinda Says New Minimum Wage to Be Announced

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-10-06T14:57:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/zambia-s-lubinda-says-new-minimum-wage-to-be-announced.html
     Oct. 6 (Bloomberg) --Zambia’s labor minister will soon
announce a new minimum wage, Given Lubinda, the country’s
information minister, told reporters in Lusaka, the capital,
today.  He called for an end to a number of strikes that are taking
place in the country.  To contact the reporter on this story:
